{"tid":701773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩幅圖已經證明香港司法有幾優勝","createTime":"2018-06-14T11:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T14:51:02.000Z","uid":143499,"like":61,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07d8f6985368fd7b64d7babf19d8d889c97da35d","tid":701773,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:23:34.000Z","msg":"Kong U:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/191701_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F191701_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=09acc9ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShitty U:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/191725_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F191725_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=86128836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n論嚴重性偷拍裸照肯定高過偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解港大精算系尖子就判感化18個月， 城大就判監18個月?<br />\n<br />\n法官又話佢哋嘅職責係以事實判案，唔會諗社會背景同個人背景為理由犯案?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天的我打倒昨天的我，就算係考慮社會背景或個人背景， 原來港大尖子就可以殺人放火金腰帶， 冇乜前途嘅city仔就要坐十幾個月監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果依啲唔係人治，我即刻切柒煲湯派街坊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港係行普通法係要講案例， 如果法官依照以前案例去判刑係需要作特別解釋同公開交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果city仔偷錢要判18個月監禁，咁我呢啲垃圾樹中仔衝紅燈咪要判三十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88271420ff32e0f92a2e9924f86c6e8d618274fa","tid":701773,"uid":18105,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"你自己睇下入屋犯法罪同不誠實使用電腦邊個嚴重d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db27f5854077e215a1da6bf14e1444a6e7fd7d5","tid":701773,"uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,